    <abstract id="aspace_0262905e8ba6909c12f50df32d14b241" label="Abstract ">Materials documenting the life and career of Charles Hamm, an advertising executive, bank president and philanthropist. Photographs, awards, collected artwork and items concerning his mother, socialite Lisbeth Higgins Hamm are included.</abstract>
